                    <msPart xml:id="p2"><msIdentifier/>
                        <msContents><summary/>
                                <msItem xml:id="p2_i1">
                                    <locus target="#1"/>
                                    <title>Fragment of an Amharic commentary to a theological text</title>
                                    <note>Taken from another manuscript and bound in as a guard leaf. The text begins ex abrupto.</note>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><gap reason="lost"/>ጨዋሂ፡ ግን፡ ከአልስማ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጌታነቱን፡ ይነሳዋል፡ የደሆችን፡ ጮሆት፡ ካልስማ፡ እርሱንም፡
                                        የለመነውን፡ አይሰማውም፡ እግዚአብሔር። ዘይፀመም፡ አእዛኒሁ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይስማዕ፡ አውያተ፡ ነ<cb n="1b"/>ዳያን።</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                        </msContents>        
